Shell Completions for btrdasd
=============================

Generate and install shell completion scripts using the built-in
`btrdasd completions` subcommand.

Bash
----
  btrdasd completions bash > /usr/share/bash-completion/completions/btrdasd

Zsh
---
  btrdasd completions zsh > /usr/local/share/zsh/site-functions/_btrdasd

Fish
----
  btrdasd completions fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/btrdasd.fish

Elvish
------
  btrdasd completions elvish > ~/.config/elvish/lib/btrdasd.elv

PowerShell
----------
  btrdasd completions powershell > _btrdasd.ps1

After installing, restart your shell or source the completion file
for changes to take effect.
